name: Jeanne Berserk (Fate Grand Order)
description:
CHECK THE NEW VERSION (SUMMER JALTER), WAY MORE ACCURATE AND CAN BE USED WITH OTHER CHECKPOINTS.

You might need to use the trigger word:

Jeanne_Berserk

I wanted to create my own Jeanne Alter LORA so here it is, it's my first try creating one so a lot of stuff might not look great, will do my best to try and updating it whenever I can.

This LORA was trained using AbyssOrangeMix3 (AOM3), it does well with anything 4.5 too, feel free to test more models.


THIS LORA DOES NOT WORK WELL WITH REALISTIC MODELS, SO COSPLAYS WILL MOSTLY LOOK ATROUCIOUS.

CLOSE-UPS AND PORTRAITS WILL BREAK THE LORA AND GIVE YOU A NIGHTMARE ENTITY!

Anything beyond 0.8 is too strong so be careful, think anything between 0.4 and 0.7 should look fine.

Please I would highly recommend you to use these TI:

badhandv4 - AnimeIllustDiffusion

EasyNegative

Deep Negative V1

veryBadImageNegative

badv3 - AnimeIllustDiffusion

modelVersions.name: Summer Jalter (FGO)
trainedWords: yellow_eyes, long hair, single thighhigh, white hair, thigh strap, bikini
modelVersions.description:
Don't forget the trigger word! IT'S DIFFERENT THIS VERSION and I will probably keep using this new word in future versions.

summer_jalter

This LORA is too strong farther away from 1.1 and too weak below 0.8, check the big image for reference.

It starts at 0.1 and ends at 1.2, from left to right, top to bottom.

Well this took a lot of tries, this version now should be good to use on most anime-like checkpoints, was trained using the NAI model.

This LORA still has some inconsistencies but the following recommended prompts and negatives should give you almost 90% accuracy for her outfit

Prompts:

yellow_eyes, long hair, single thighhigh, white hair, thigh strap, bikini

If somehow you can't get the high heels to show properly just use:

open toe high heels

Negative prompts:

dress, animal ears, towel, skirt, cape, nylon, black thigh high, swimsuit, black hair, leotard, skirt, one piece swimsuit, coat, long gloves

I would strongly recommend you to use the negative prompts, specially "swimsuit" and "one piece swimsuit". Somehow without these two you might get part of her belly covered with different clothes.

That's it, thanks for the feedback on the previous model, really learned a lot from that one.
